      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 employed under a 21 CFR Part 11-compliant quality management system. All input files version-controlled in Git; automated regression suite confirmed no solver-version regressions. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2 for Medium model risk."
