      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted (coarse 1.2 mm, medium 0.8 mm, fine 0.5 mm global seed at screw-rod interface). Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI of 1.8% for stiffness and 2.3% for yield force. Fine mesh selected for all production runs. Achieved level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
