      "rationale": "Force and displacement residuals converged to 1e-6 for all 13 load steps in each of the 11 model instances. Energy residual remained below 0.01% throughout. No solver warnings or divergence events observed. Achieved level 2 exceeds required level 1."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of modeling assumptions, boundary conditions, and material assignments completed by a second analyst not involved in model construction.",
      "rationale": "A senior FDA OSEL analyst independent of the primary modeler reviewed all boundary conditions, contact definitions, material assignments, and load application. One minor error in constraint reference frame corrected prior to final runs. Final model confirmed correct. Meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
